            <LEXSense LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="2021-10-22 12:06:40" LastEditedBy="">
              <DefinitionLong/>
              <DefinitionShort>act of deciding a question of legal right or wrong, and thus determining the innocence or guilt of the accused and assigning appropriate punishment or retribution{N:001}</DefinitionShort>
